components.description: API for client code that uses random numbers generators.

components.description: Simple API for instantiating random numbers generators.

components.name: commons-rng-core
components.description: Pure Java implementations of random numbers generator algorithms. Code in this module should not be used directly by applications; please use the client interface defined in module "commons-rng-client-api" and the factory methods defined in module "commons-rng-simple". In a future release, modularization may be enforced through JPMS access restrictions.

components.name: commons-rng-sampling
components.description: The Apache Commons RNG Sampling module provides samplers for various distributions.
